OL,3,CRenovate houses rather than build new
OL,4,Cones, argues Tameside landlord
OL,6,FEmma Sweeney spoke to landlord Stephen
OL,7,FGoodison who says landlords should be
OL,8,Furged to renovate empty properties
OL,10,FA landlord who claims there are more
OL,11,Fthan 500 abandoned homes in his local
OL,12,Farea is calling on the Government and
OL,13,Flocal authorities to encourage
OL,14,Flandlords to renovate unused
OL,15,Fproperties to help tackle a lack of
OL,16,Faffordable housing.
