OL,3,CRenovate houses rather than build new
OL,4,Cones, argues Tameside landlord
OL,6,FStephen Goodison manages properties in
OL,7,FGreater Manchester and Tameside, and
OL,8,Fsays Angela Rayner's promise of
OL,9,Fbuilding one and a half million new
OL,10,Fhomes is a "pure fantasy."
OL,12,FInstead, Stephen is arguing that
OL,13,Flandlords should be encouraged to
OL,14,Frenovate and repurpose their empty
OL,15,Fproperties.
OL,17,FHe's calling on local authorities to
OL,18,Fput in place empty dwelling management
OL,19,Forders, giving them management of the
OL,20,Fproperty.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
