OL,3,CRenovate houses rather than build new
OL,4,Cones, argues Tameside landlord
OL,6,FRachel Reeves' Autumn budget included
OL,7,F#5 billion of investment to help fund
OL,8,FLabour's manifesto pledge to build 1.5
OL,9,Fmillion homes over the course of this
OL,10,FParliament.
OL,12,FSome #500 million will fund the
OL,13,Fbuilding of new social housing
OL,14,Fproperties, and a further #128 million
OL,15,Ffor three new projects to build more
OL,16,Fhomes - some of which will be energy
OL,17,Fefficient.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
