OL,3,CRenovate houses rather than build new
OL,4,Cones, argues Tameside landlord
OL,6,FShe said: "We will provide #3 billion
OL,7,Fof support in guarantees to boost the
OL,8,Fsupply of homes and support our
OL,9,Fsmaller housebuilders," she said.
OL,11,F"And we will provide investment to
OL,12,Frenovate sites across our country,
OL,13,Fincluding at Liverpool Central Docks,
OL,14,Fwhere we will deliver 2,000 new homes,
OL,15,Fand funding to help Cambridge realise
OL,16,Fits full growth potential."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
