OL,3,CRenovate houses rather than build new
OL,4,Cones, argues Tameside landlord
OL,6,FClaire Bayley is a mother-of-five who
OL,7,Fhas experienced homelessness and
OL,8,Fstruggled to find a suitable home. She
OL,9,Fhopes the investment in housing will
OL,10,Fmake it easier for people like her.
OL,12,FShe said: "When I was applying for
OL,13,Fhouses there was like 200 people going
OL,14,Ffor one house. It's just unrealistic.
OL,16,F"I was lucky enough to have a friend
OL,17,Fwho had a privately rented property
OL,18,Fthat I'm in now... I'm really grateful
OL,19,Fbut some people just aren't that lucky.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
