OL,3,CRenovate houses rather than build new
OL,4,Cones, argues Tameside landlord
OL,6,FIt's hoped the increased tax rate will
OL,7,Fincentivise property owners to either
OL,8,Frent out or sell their houses.
OL,10,FWell responding to the points raised
OL,11,Fby Stephen, a government spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid: "Councils have a range of tools
OL,13,Fat their disposal to bring empty homes
OL,14,Fback into use, including charging
OL,15,Fadditional council tax on vacant
OL,16,Fproperties.
